Third-party data bundled with Open Pedigree
===========================================

disorders.json — Orphanet rare disease nomenclature
---------------------------------------------------
Source:      Orphanet / Orphadata — https://www.orphadata.com/ (en_product1.xml)
Licence:     Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
             https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
Attribution: Orphanet. INSERM 1997. An online rare disease and orphan drug data base.
             Available at https://www.orpha.net/. Accessed 2026-06.

Contains the Orphanet nomenclature (ORPHAcode + disease name). Chinese names are machine
translations of the Orphanet English names, produced by us; they are a derivative of the
CC BY material above and carry no endorsement by Orphanet. Orphanet classification
categories (disorder_type = "Category") are excluded — they are headings, not diagnoses.

Built by desktop/build/make-disorders.py.


