NOT bundled: OMIM
-----------------
OMIM (https://omim.org/) is copyrighted by Johns Hopkins University and its terms do not
permit redistributing the database inside an application. Disorder suggestions therefore
come from Orphanet only. A pedigree may still *reference* an OMIM MIM number (typed as
free text, or imported from a file); the desktop build simply cannot resolve it to a name
offline, and shows the number instead.
